PRIVACY POLICY
Last update: January 18, 2023
We are committed to protecting and maintaining the confidentiality and integrity of the personal data and information (hereinafter “
Data
”) of our users. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, process, use, or otherwise handle the data provided or collected through our own channels or on channels made available through us on third-party platforms. This Privacy Policy applies to your access and/or use of our website (https://klinkfinance.com) as well as any other media form, mobile website or mobile application that is related, linked, or otherwise connected thereto (hereinafter our “
Platform
”).
By using and accessing our Platform, you agree to be bound by this Privacy Policy and our Terms of Service. Therefore, it is important that you read this Privacy Policy with our Cookies Policy and any other notices we may provide to you on specific occasions to inform you about the details of your data being processed or collected by us. However, if you are a user of our Platform, this Privacy Policy applies together with any other contractual documents we may have with you. Please note that our Platform is not intended for minors below the age of 18 years, and we do not knowingly collect data relating to minors.
