DATA MINING
You shall not use, scan, capture or otherwise share information on our Services and/or Platform, or otherwise use any data-mining technology to conduct any non-authorised activity, and shall not allow its agent or subcontractors to do the same. Data mining is strictly prohibited. Any violation of such would make you liable to Applicable Laws.
SUBLICENSING
Except as expressly provided through a written agreement granting consent for sub-licensing for any rights, a Licensee shall not grant sublicense to any agent, subcontractor or other third party. Incase of such consent, the Licensee shall be responsible for the conduct of all sub-licensees and the operations of all sub-licensees shall be deemed to be the operations of the Licensee.
